Interface PsiNameValuePair

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface PsiNameValuePair
extends PsiElement, JvmAnnotationAttribute
    Represents a single element-value pair of an annotation parameter list.
    See Also:
    PsiAnnotation, PsiAnnotationParameterList

      • getDetachedValue

        default PsiAnnotationMemberValue getDetachedValue()
        Returns:
        a element representing the annotation attribute's value. The main difference to getValue() is that this method avoids expensive AST loading (see StubBasedPsiElementBase doc). The downside is that the result might not be in the same tree as the parent, might be non-physical and so should only be used for read operations.
